foreignObject.div: Things are wrong in user space

# slow system calls
sysdig -c topscalls
sysdig -c bottlenecks
sysdig -c scallslower

# are you busy reading from disk
pidstat -h -d -t -p pid

# are you busy context switching
pidtstat -h -w -t -p pid

# are you busy with page faults
pidtstat -h -r -t -p pid

# check CPU caches and IPC
perf
